<plot>A woman, who thought her husband had committed suicide, discovers that he was actually alive for the past six years. She finds out that his crazy sister put a hit on her years earlier and her husband killed the hit man and faked his own death in order to protect her. With his new life in Chicago, he starts importing illegal drugs with his sister. When he gets cold feet, he turns up dead, and it's up to Jean to find out the truth once and for all.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?335340</url></doc>
